Norwegian explanation: Reduserer energibehov til romoppvarming med 7 % for bygg opp til TEK10. 2 % for TEK17.
Explanation: Reduces space heating demand by 7 % for buildings up to TEK10. 2 % for TEK17. In the column names is this shortened to “small measure”.

Norwegian explanation: Reduserer energibehov til oppvarming med 20 % for bygg opp til TEK10. 5 % for TEK17.
Explanation: Reduces space heating demand by 20 % for buildings up to TEK10. 5 % for TEK17.

Norwegian explanation: Reduserer energibehov til romoppvarming med 25 % for bygg opp til TEK10. 7 % for TEK17.
Explanation: Reduces space heating demand by 25 % for buildings up to TEK10. 7 % for TEK17.

Norwegian explanation: Enebolig, rekkehus, tomannsbolig, firemannsbolig.
Explanation: Residential buildings which are not multi-storey apartment blocks.

Norwegian explanation: Bygningsarealet har ikke utført enøk eller rehabilitering.
Explanation: The floor area/building has not completed any measures.

Norwegian explanation: En boligblokk inneholder flere leligheter.
Explanation: Residential apartments. An apartment block contains multiple apartments.

Norwegian explanation: De 11 bygningskategoriene I TEK som ikke er boliger.
Explanation: The 11 building categories in the building code that are not residential buildings.

Norwegian explanation: Energibærer.
Explanation: Energy product.

Norwegian explanation: Oppvarmingsteknologi, punktoppvarming. For eksempel panelovn eller vifteovn.
Explanation: Heating technology, space heating. For example electrical panel heater or convection oven.

Norwegian explanation: Oppvarmingsteknologi som bruker ved. Punktoppvarming.
Explanation: Heating technology using fuel wood. Space heating.

Norwegian explanation: Punktoppvarming, kan ikke varme opp hele bygningen med én enhet.
Explanation: Point source and cannot heat an entire building with one unit.

Norwegian explanation: Varmtvannsbereder for varmt tappevann.
Explanation: Electric water heater for domestic hot water.

Norwegian explanation: Vannbåren varme.
Explanation: Water-borne heating.

Norwegian explanation: Vannbåren varme.
Explanation: Water-borne heating.

Norwegian explanation: Vannbåren varme.
Explanation: Water-borne heating.

Norwegian explanation: Vannbåren varme.
Explanation: Water-borne heating.

Norwegian explanation: Samlebegrep for alle varmepumper som leverer vannbåren varme.
Explanation: Term for all heat pumps that delivers water-borne heating.

Norwegian explanation: Vannbåren varme. Hentet fra SSB sin fjernvarmestatistikk for kalibrering.
Explanation: Water-borne heating. Uses Statistics Norways district heating statistics for calibration.

Norwegian explanation: Energiforbruk som krever elektrisitet, som belysning. Kan ikke erstattes med andre energivarer.
Explanation: Electricity usage which cannot be replaced by another technology or energy product. Like lighting and electrical appliances.

Norwegian explanation: Kjøleteknologi. Bruker elektrisitet.
Explanation: Cooling technology. Uses electricity.

Norwegian explanation: Arealet har en av fem tilstander: uberørt, gjennomført enøk, gjennomført rehabilitering, gjennomført enøk og rehabilitering eller revet.
Explanation: The heated floor area will be in of five conditions: original, completed small measures, completed rehabilitation, completed small measures and rehabilitation or demolished.

Norwegian explanation: Omfatter kun lagerbygg i modellen. En underkategori av lettindustri og verksted.
Explanation: Consists only of storage and warehouses in the model. A subcategory of light industry and workshops.

Norwegian explanation: Arealets energibehov i kWh/m2 etter definisjon i TEK. Teoretisk størrelse.
Explanation: The areas energy need in kWh/m\ :sup:`2` after definition in the building code. A theoretical size.

Norwegian explanation: Den energimengden arealet må få tilført for å dekke energibehovet. Målbar mengde. I kWh/m\ :sup:`2`. Dette er en målbar mengde.
Explanation: The amount of delivered energy the area requires in order to cover the energy need. In kWh/m\ :sup:`2` This is a measurable quantity.

Norwegian explanation: Energivaren til oppvarmingsteknologien.
Explanation: Energy product used by the heating technology.
